\section desc Description
<!-- Short description of what this package is supposed to provide -->

The ShmBuffer package implementes the communication via shared memory
between the evf::FUResourceBroker and one or many
evf::FUEventProcessors on a Filter Farm Node.

The architecture of the Filter Farm is described <a
href="https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/view/CMS/FilterUnitDesign">here</a>.

The ShmBuffer package is documented <a
href="https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/view/CMS/FUShmBuffer">here</a>.


\subsection interface Public interface
<!-- List the classes that are provided for use in other packages (if any) -->

- evf::FUShmBuffer
- evf::FUShmDqmCell
- evf::FUShmRawCell
- evf::FUShmRecoCell


\subsection modules Modules
<!-- Describe modules implemented in this package and their parameter set -->
No modules are defined by this package.

\subsection tests Unit tests and examples

 <!-- Describe cppunit tests and example configuration files -->

The executables FUShmserver_t and FUShmClient_t demonstrate the basic
functionality of the inter-process communication via shared memory.

FUShmCleanup_t releases shared memory segments which might be left
behind by these example applications.


